%% Current State: HW Feature-Driven Design Change
flowchart TD
classDef gate fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#c0392b,color:#fff
classDef milestone fill:#2ecc71,stroke:#27ae60,color:#fff
classDef feedback fill:#f39c12,stroke:#e67e22,color:#fff
classDef process fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#90caf9,color:#1a237e
classDef artifact fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#ffcc02,color:#333
classDef external fill:#e0e0e0,stroke:#9e9e9e,color:#333

start([Feature or customization need]) --> identify[HW Engineer identifies change]
identify --> discuss[Discuss in standup or design meeting]
discuss --> informal{Informal approval?}
informal -->|Yes| change[Make hardware change]
informal -->|No| refine[Refine approach offline]
refine --> discuss
change --> review[Informal peer review]
review --> update(Update notes or drawing)
update --> done((Change used in build))

class start,done external
class identify,discuss,change,review process
class informal gate
class refine feedback
class update artifact
